testimonial: I am very grateful to BT Navi Mumbai for helping me achieve a good rank in JEE Mains & JEE Advanced. The teachers were very hands-on with teaching and doubt clearing, and they were exceptional at making topics easily understandable. The test series also helped me improve my confidence and marks. BT Navi Mumbai had an enormous influence on me getting a good rank in JEE Advanced 2025.

I am truly thankful to my teachers and the entire Bakliwal Tutorials team. The knowledge they shared, along with their motivation and study tips, truly made a difference in my journey. The regular mock tests at BT were extremely helpful and relevant. They showed me where I stood and helped me boost my exam temperament. The teachers were always ready to help with my doubts, and their support made my success possible.

Joining BT has been an amazing journey for me. The teachers, study materials, and support helped me grow and stay focused. I learned how to work hard and stay strong during tough times. BT made my dream possible, and I'm really thankful for everything it has given me.

Bakliwal Tutorials provided me with the right platform for great learning and performance during the JEE examination. Their efficient testing system helped me gauge my preparedness level and identify areas for improvement. The one-on-one doubt-clearing sessions were also a tremendous help. The teachers helped me with complex problems, which ultimately clarified my concepts. I am truly grateful for their unwavering guidance and support.

My name is Eshan Bausal, and I joined BT for the most important year of my prep. From the day I joined, I fell in love with the quality of questions in the BT modules. My teachers were always approachable and never hesitated to explain even my "silliest of doubts". The BT Test Series had new and challenging questions that pushed my limits and helped me face the completely new JEE Advanced questions. Overall, I had a great and fulfilling experience at Bakliwal Tutorials.

I am very grateful to my teachers, Girish Sir and Parth Sir, at BT. They provided invaluable advice and guidance throughout my preparation journey. The mock tests at BT were filled with new and challenging questions, helping me with time management. My journey at BT was a very sweet, fruitful, and memorable one.
I owe a huge part of my success to the faculties at Bakliwal Tutorials. The journey here was fantastic, and their constant support and guidance greatly helped me during my journey to success.
